      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. but the crisis lines... they don't get it. they just try to talk you out of how you feel. it's not that i'm \"in crisis\" in a sudden way, it's just that this is my life now. every single day is a battle i'm losing. doesn't it feel a bit cruel that life just forces you to keep going even when the quality of life is just pure, unadulterated misery?",
